description:
PilotsEYE.tv Los Angeles "Premiere in Jumbo format"

For the first time, PilotsEYE.tv is a guest in the cockpit of a Boeing 747-400 and accompanies the ruler over 710 aircraft and 1700 pilots into aeronautical retirement. PilotsEYE shows the most spectacular images from the cockpit of airliners and guarantees unusual authentic insights into the real everyday life of a pilot in HD quality.

I figured out how to encode with more than one subtitle so this file includes both German and English subtitles

Encoded in 1080p format

Fellow aviation lovers, enjoy!
